<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer { padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to {{companyName}}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Welcome aboard! Your HRMS account has been created successfully.</p>
      <p><strong>Your login details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: {{email}}</li>
        <li>Employee Code: {{employeeCode}}</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Please log in and update your password at your earliest convenience.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>HR Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from {{companyName}} HRMS.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
